  "text": "3) C r Image Component: Our system gave the best result for C r image component in image splicing detection. In Table III we present the confusion matrix of C r image component based on 158 images from CASIA dataset [1] The results of the C r component show that we achieved True-Positive (TP) rate about 99%, and True-Negative (TN) rate grater than 71%. The False-Positive (FP) rate is 29%, and the False-Negative (FN) rate is just 1%.According to [CITATION_1] C r component showed accuracy up to 90.5% which is less than our result by 8.5%.",
